returns the configuration. (This method is defined in the ConfigProviderInterface , although explicitly implementing this interface in the
module class is optional.) This method should return either an  array  or a Traversable  object. Continue by editing  module/Blog/src/Module.php :  // In /module/Blog/Module.php:
class Module
{
