    ],
];  The above configuration tells the application that the folder module/Blog/view/  has view files in it that match the above described default
scheme. It is important to note that with this you can not only ship view files
for your module, but you can also overwrite view files from other modules.  Reload your site now. Finally we are at a point where we see something different
